thumb.title: M. Tyrrell Burrus, MD
thumb.description: Dr. M. Tyrrell Burrus is a Board Certified orthopedic surgeon with fellowship training in sports medicine and shoulder surgery treating patients in multiple locations throughout Austin, Texas and surrounding areas. He specializes in operative and non-operative management of complex shoulder and knee injuries.M.
